onchain_metadata.name: Gerolamo Dots #141
History: Gerolamo Cardano was the first to describe hypocycloids,
the pointed plane curves generated by the trace of a fixed point
on a small circle that rolls within a larger circle,
and the generating circles were later named
Description: that represent the mathematics behind the Cardano logo.
